Subject: virtio-blk: Fix WARN_ON_ONCE in virtio_queue_rq()

From: Suwan Kim <suwan.kim027@gmail.com>

[ Upstream commit 37fafe6b61e4f15d977982635bb785f4e605f7cd ]

